(543, 1, '2014-02-05 19:09:53', '2014-02-05 19:09:53', '<strong>MYDM</strong>, by Phai Subhawita Klunson, is a bangkok-based graphic design house offering a variety of creative branding and design services for a wide range of private and corporate clients who value our refined and detail visuals. To get the finest execution, we craft the concept and develop beautiful and honest graphic out of our sincere care. We are also a home to Crafting and Design Community; we''d love to share our belief to others. MYDM items are designed to stimulate ones'' creative thinking and empower them to make their mark of how to create the happy home living lifestyle in the crazy world.\r\n\r\n[column_one_third]\r\n[lightbox media_type="image" thumbnail_url="http://mydm.me/2013/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/ABOUT_team_01_Phai.jpg" url="http://mydm.me/2013/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/ABOUT_team_01_Phai.jpg" rollover_text="Brand Design Director" width="100%" height="auto" align="left"][/lightbox]\r\n<h5>PHAI SUBHAWITA KLUNSORN</h5>\r\n<h6>Brand Design Director</h6>\r\nWith hands-on-experience in many fields ie., literature, culinary, import-export, visual merchandising, and graphic design. Prior to Suya, her previous employer includes Stuart Design and Phil R. Cohen Associates in Chicago. Phai will ensure the highest standards of graphic output.\r\n[/column_one_third][column_one_third]\r\n[lightbox media_type="image" thumbnail_url="http://mydm.me/2013/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/ABOUT_team_02_Pui.jpg" url="http://mydm.me/2013/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/ABOUT_team_02_Pui.jpg" rollover_text="Senior Graphic Designer" width="100%" height="auto" align="left"][/lightbox]\r\n<h5>PUI SIRILAK</h5>\r\n<h6>Senior Graphic Designer</h6>\r\nWe dance for laughter, we dance for tears, We dance for madness, We dance for fears. We dance for hopes, We dance for screams, We are the dancers, and we create the dreams.\r\n[/column_one_third][column_one_third_last]\r\n[lightbox media_type="image" thumbnail_url="http://mydm.me/2013/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/ABOUT_team_03_Ae.jpg" url="http://mydm.me/2013/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/ABOUT_team_03_Ae.jpg" rollover_text="Content Editor" width="100%" height="auto" align="left"][/lightbox]\r\n<h5>AE YADA</h5>\r\n<h6>Content Editor</h6>\r\nDonec sed odio dui. Duis mollis, est non commodo luctus, nisi erat porttitor ligula, eget lacinia odio sem nec elit. Sed posuere consectetur est at lobortis.\r\n[/column_one_third_last][column_one_third][lightbox media_type="image" thumbnail_url="http://mydm.me/2013/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/ABOUT_team_04_Katang.jpg" url="http://mydm.me/2013/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/ABOUT_team_04_Katang.jpg" rollover_text="Office Manager" width="100%" height="auto" align="left"][/lightbox]\r\n<h5>KATANG RUNG-A-ROON</h5>\r\n<h6>Office Manager</h6>\r\nStay true to you and you will end up incredibly happy\r\n[/column_one_third][column_one_third][lightbox media_type="image" thumbnail_url="http://mydm.me/2013/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/ABOUT_team_05_lookkaew.jpg" url="http://mydm.me/2013/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/ABOUT_team_05_lookkaew.jpg" rollover_text="Graphic Designer" width="100%" height="auto" align="left"][/lightbox]\r\n<h5>LOOKKAEW SIRARUT</h5>\r\n<h6>Graphic Designer</h6>\r\nLorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Donec iaculis metus vitae ligula elementum ut luctus lorem facilisis. Sed non leo nisl, ac euismod nisi. Aenean\r\n[/column_one_third][column_one_third_last][lightbox media_type="image" thumbnail_url="http://mydm.me/2013/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/ABOUT_team_06_view.jpg" url="http://mydm.me/2013/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/ABOUT_team_06_view.jpg" rollover_text="Graphic Designer" width="100%" height="auto" align="left"][/lightbox]\r\n<h5>VIEW PRATTHANA</h5>\r\n<h6>Graphic Designer</h6>\r\nWorking hard for something we don’t care about is called stress. Working hard for something we love called passion.\r\n[/column_one_third_last]\r\n[image url="http://mydm.me/2013/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/ABOUT_team_07_MYDM.jpg" width="100%" height="auto" align="left" caption_style="single-border" caption_width="500px" caption_align="center"]www.mydm.me[/image]', 'About', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '16-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-02-05 19:09:53', '2014-02-05 19:09:53', '', 16, 'http://mydm.me/2013/%e0%b9%84%e0%b8%a1%e0%b9%88%e0%b8%a1%e0%b8%b5%e0%b8%ab%e0%b8%a1%e0%b8%a7%e0%b8%94%e0%b8%ab%e0%b8%a1%e0%b8%b9%e0%b9%88/16-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
